2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed algorithm involves the use of quantum mechanics principles, which is a subfield of AI. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the use of the QDDS algorithm for solving the multidimensional FIR filter design problem, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The QDDS algorithm can be seen as a type of machine learning algorithm for optimization problems. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the performance of the QDDS algorithm on benchmark functions, which is a common approach in algorithm analysis and falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms.
